# HMError.Code.invalidAssociatedServiceType

**Case**

An error indicating an invalid service type.

## Declaration

```swift
case invalidAssociatedServiceType
```

## Association errors

- **HMError.Code.objectAlreadyAssociatedToHome**: An attempt to associate an object with a home when it’s already associated with that home.
- **HMError.Code.objectAssociatedToAnotherHome**: An attempt to associate an object with a home when it’s already associated with another home.
- **HMError.Code.objectNotAssociatedToAnyHome**: An attempt to perform an operation on an object that is not associated to any home.
